value.string: Freshly painted and very well maintained, this ground floor unit has all new stainless steel appliances, and is in a very private setting. Ready for your personal style to make this your home. Wailea Palms has one of the most beautiful pool pavilions with a large pool and spa, bar-b-que and party pavilion area, and an air conditioned workout room with weights, cardio, everything you need. Just a short stroll a block away is Keawakapu Beach, rated the #1 beach in the world by Condo Nast Travel Magazine, and a short drive to world class golfing, shopping, and restaurants.

Location is the key to enjoying the Maui Lifestyle. This 1 bed, 2 bath, ground floor, very private Ekahi condominium walks out to a lush landscape of bougainvillea and palm trees swaying in the trade winds that most days offer. Just a short distance to the lower pool pavilion and the Wailea Beach Walk which allows you to stroll along the ocean in front of all of Wailea's luxury resorts. This condominium is very clean with an updated master bath and a gorgeous Koa wood, built in book case. You can look long and hard to find an ocean front condominium under $1 Million with features and amenities like Ekahi. Call you favorite Realtor for a private showing today! WCA dues are voluntary.

Single level beautifully maintained renovated two bedroom, two bath condo in the gated Wailea Palms Private Residences. The community recreation pavilion enjoys a beautiful ocean view pool with hot tub, fitness center, BBQs and entertaining center. Wailea amenities apply.
